data.description: Great opportunity in the charming town of Phelan! Find this large 2,440 sqft home featuring 3-bedrooms, 2-bathrooms, and an attached 2-car garage! Enter the home into an open-concept living space showcasing gorgeous flooring, a large bright window, a wet bar, and beautiful stone fireplace. Open to the living space is the kitchen equipped with tons of cabinet space, glossy countertops, recessed lighting, and bar seating. Bedrooms are good-sized with cozy carpet flooring. The home is on a huge 2.27 acre lot dotted with gorgeous trees and views of snow-capped mountains in the distance. So many possibilities! Do not miss out.
